                            </p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div>
                        <div
                            class="relative border border-[#F7D243] shadow-md rounded-xl p-6 text-center mt-8"
                        >
                            <div
                                class="circle-icon absolute -top-6 left-1/2 -translate-x-1/2 w-14 h-14 rounded-full bg-gradient-to-b from-purple-400 to-indigo-600 flex items-center justify-center shadow-lg"
                            >
                                <img
                                    src={OwnBuying.src}
                                    alt="Own Crypto"
                                    width="24px"
                                />
                            </div>

                            <h5 class="text-[22px] font-bold mt-5">
                                Own Instead of Buying
                            </h5>
                            <p>
                                Generate your own coins instead of purchasing
                                them on exchanges, boosting long-term value.
                            </p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div>
                        <div
                            class="relative border border-[#F7D243] shadow-md rounded-xl p-6 text-center mt-8"
                        >
                            <div
                                class="circle-icon absolute -top-6 left-1/2 -translate-x-1/2 w-14 h-14 rounded-full bg-gradient-to-b from-purple-400 to-indigo-600 flex items-center justify-center shadow-lg"
                            >
                                <img
                                    src={Expense.src}
                                    alt="Expense"
                                    width="24px"
                                />
                            </div>

                            <h5 class="text-[22px] font-bold mt-5">
                                Expense, Not Investment
                            </h5>
                            <p>
                                Treat mining costs as operational expenses
